&lt;p&gt;ロビーからテラスに出たところ&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a data-flickr-embed=&#34;true&#34;  href=&#34;https://www.flickr.com/photos/nobu666/26210414463/in/dateposted-public/&#34; title=&#34;IMG_7199&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7063/26210414463_417e988d80_z.jpg&#34; width=&#34;640&#34; height=&#34;427&#34; alt=&#34;IMG_7199&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;script async src=&#34;//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js&#34; charset=&#34;utf-8&#34;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

